## Tile.loadingFinished() method

Called by the \[\[TileLoader\]\] after the `Tile` has finished loading its map data. Can be used to add content to the `Tile`<!-- -->. The \[\[DecodedTile\]\] should still be available.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
loadingFinished(): void;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

void
